# UI Constraints

## Rule 2: Mobile-First Constraint

- Assume mobile-first rendering
- Desktop appearance must remain visually identical unless overflow or clipping occurs

## Rule 3: No Framework Injection

- Do not introduce Tailwind, Bootstrap, or any CSS framework
- Do not replace existing CSS with utility-based styling

## Rule 4: Demo-Safety Verification

- After every change, mentally verify rendering at: **375px**, **768px**, **1024px**, **1440px**
- If any uncertainty exists, choose the safer visual option
